  "body": "### Description\n\nFor native builds, whenever someone passes enables debug info (e.g. `-Dquarkus.native.debug.enabled`), the Maven/Gradle plugins should inject the `dependency:sources` target. Otherwise only the source code for JDK/GraalVM and the application would be included. None of the Quarkus and any other dependency sources would be there, making debugging with tools such as `gdb` potentially problematic.\r\n\r\nSee https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/31118 for more details.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
